    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Asymmetrical seating forms with gently curved backs and having one arm higher than the other; made especially during the French Empire period.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
